44:00.531 --> 44:06.503
♪ pressure on people,
people on streets ♪

44:06.537 --> 44:11.240
♪ turned away from it all
like a blind man ♪

44:11.258 --> 44:15.045
♪ sat on a fence,
but it don't work ♪

44:15.079 --> 44:18.748
♪ keep coming up with love
but it's so slashed and torn ♪

44:18.766 --> 44:22.018
♪ why, why

44:22.053 --> 44:25.889
♪ why-y?

