01:21:07.819 --> 01:21:11.238
♪ while looking
for my big break ♪

01:21:11.273 --> 01:21:13.574
♪

01:21:13.608 --> 01:21:16.977
♪ some gentlemen
opened doors ♪

01:21:16.995 --> 01:21:22.249
♪ but once inside,
they were all on the make ♪

01:21:22.284 --> 01:21:25.485
♪ to sparkle,
I lit a match ♪

01:21:25.504 --> 01:21:30.207
♪ and I admit
some bridges were burned ♪

01:21:30.258 --> 01:21:34.295
Both: ♪ oh, but we won't flop
