01:21:38.216 --> 01:21:43.137
♪ uh, give 'em that big finish

01:21:43.171 --> 01:21:46.974
♪ and they'll forget
what came before ♪

01:21:47.008 --> 01:21:52.679
♪ just give 'em
that big finish ♪

01:21:52.697 --> 01:21:56.734
♪ but always keep
one eye on the door ♪

01:21:56.785 --> 01:22:01.155
♪ so I give this lesson
to you, my friend ♪

01:22:01.189 --> 01:22:06.710
♪ they'll forgive and forget
