01:22:06.745 --> 01:22:12.800
Both: ♪ just give 'em
that big finish ♪

01:22:12.834 --> 01:22:15.636
♪ and leave them wanting more

01:22:15.670 --> 01:22:21.675
♪

01:22:35.357 --> 01:22:38.943
♪ you struggle
from step to step ♪

01:22:38.994 --> 01:22:44.415
♪ just praying
you find the one ♪

01:22:44.449 --> 01:22:47.785
♪ the love that you want
disappears ♪

01:22:47.836 --> 01:22:53.540
♪ as the love that you need
settles in for a run ♪

01:22:53.574 --> 01:22:56.677
♪ you think that you're
down for the count ♪

01:22:56.711 --> 01:23:01.131
♪ but then just like a Phoenix
you rise ♪

01:23:01.182 --> 01:23:03.550
Both: ♪ and with some help
from above ♪

01:23:03.584 --> 01:23:05.686
- ♪ be it Tonys
- ♪ or love

01:23:05.720 --> 01:23:08.939
both: ♪ you'll be leaving
