01:23:14.112 --> 01:23:17.781
♪ you just forget
what came before ♪

01:23:17.816 --> 01:23:23.621
♪ just give 'em that
big finish ♪

01:23:23.655 --> 01:23:27.992
♪ and who knows what next year
has in store? ♪

01:23:28.043 --> 01:23:30.610
♪ Though the story
is finished ♪

01:23:30.629 --> 01:23:32.579
♪ we'll keep dreaming on

01:23:32.613 --> 01:23:35.049
♪ and though
we're sure to miss ♪

01:23:35.083 --> 01:23:36.750
Both: ♪ our song

01:23:36.784 --> 01:23:41.621
♪ when it's go-one

01:23:41.640 --> 01:23:46.960
♪ let's give 'em that
big finish ♪

01:23:46.978 --> 01:23:51.098
♪ and leave them wanting more

01:23:51.132 --> 01:23:54.568
♪ hear the angels shout
